    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168450/extras/7aee3ed8d805e65dbcd1a2aa7bcbfcdb.poster.avif?t=1752883580\" width=512 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168450/extras/7aee3ed8d805e65dbcd1a2aa7bcbfcdb.webm?t=1752883580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168450/extras/7aee3ed8d805e65dbcd1a2aa7bcbfcdb.mp4?t=1752883580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get into the cockpit in <strong>Packet Loss</strong>, a challenging flight simulator where precision and skill are paramount! You're a pilot tasked with transporting vital packets from one location to another. But beware - this isn't your typical delivery service. With <strong>near realistic physics and flight controls</strong>, such as using the ground effect to gain power and save fuel, every subtle adjustment, and every turn of the ship will impact your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > B<strong>alance the cargo, packets and oil drums correctly onto your ship, or <i>be prepared for potential unscheduled pedestrian transit.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168450/extras/7df427dff1b1d406ba27977b6123a0ac.poster.avif?t=1752883580\" width=512 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168450/extras/7df427dff1b1d406ba27977b6123a0ac.webm?t=1752883580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168450/extras/7df427dff1b1d406ba27977b6123a0ac.mp4?t=1752883580\" type